TITLE: Episode 62 - As Grassroots As It Gets, with @wabisabipermaculture
DESCRIPTION: A fellow anarchist yogi found Maddie on IG (we exist!) so she and Jessie had on the lovely Embry from @wabisabipermaculture to discuss the basics surrounding permaculture, sustainable living, food science, and how growing liberty starts in your own backyards.
